com.github.wuic.engine
Class EngineRequest

java.lang.Object
  com.github.wuic.engine.EngineRequest

public final class EngineRequest
extends Object

This class represents a request to be indicated to an engine.

The user which invokes Engine.parse(EngineRequest) should indicates in the parameter the nuts to be parsed and the context path to use to expose the generated nuts.

Since:
0.3.0
Version:
1.4
Author:
Guillaume DROUET
